			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Id like to expand the thread on the ultimate group.  Im definatly not an expert, so grain of salt for you if you disagree.  <BR>
<BR>
1) Tank for going toe to toe w/mobs, and allowing others do do their thing.<BR>
2) Druid for buffs, snares, damage shields, and healing.<BR>
3) Bard can regen mana and a whole slew of other abilities, bard is crucial to group.<BR>
4) Wizard for good old fasioned fire power.<BR>
<BR>
I am of the opinion that this group would be the most capable to deal with an array of situations, and although adding others would be nice, these classes at the core would be very formidable... Okay go ahead and flame me....
